  "event_name": "Map & Compass Session",
  "venue_name": "Discovery Park",
  "event_notes": "10am at Discovery Park (Administration Building). Basic map & compass course; no charge; bring a compass if you have one.\n\nWinter schedule (Dec 1978) notes: workshop concentrates on map and compass work; basic meet. Workshop in main building just inside West Government Way entrance; look for control points. Free.\n\nMar/Apr 1979 recap: ~1 hour of instruction in Discovery Park visitors' center, followed by a short (0.8 km, 5 control) course in the SE corner of the park. Meet map was extensively field-corrected; published scale 1:2500.",
